properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 4 at 4:03PM EST until January 5 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 kt with occasional gusts to
gale force and seas building to around 8 feet.

* WHERE...Flagler Beach to Volusia-Brevard County Line 0-20 nm,
Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 0-20 nm and
Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...For the Gale Warning, until 10 AM EST Sunday. For the
Small Craft Advisory, until 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for gale conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST THIS EVENING... ...GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM EST SUNDAY
